videos.headline: Boston elated with Gamecocks' share of SEC title
videos.description: Following a 67-53 win over No. 12 Tennessee to clinch a share of the regular-season SEC title, No. 1 South Carolina's Aliyah Boston discusses the "amazing" feeling.
